---
title: Double Mumbai White Fish & Cauliflower Curry with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: This deeply flavourful fish and cauliflower curry is like a golden sunset. Filled to the brim with bright veggies and
tender white fish, we reckon this beaming bowl will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night.
